## Entity Hierarchy

In BeeHero, `group_id` == `beekeeper_id`. This repo covers **Beekeeper groups only**.

```
group_id  (beekeeper)
  └── yard_id
        └── sensor_mac_address  (one sensor per hive)
              └── gateway_mac_address  (sensors report via a gateway)
```

