### 2. Hive Updates Query (Athena — raw DB)

Queried via `hive_updates_query()` from `src/model_monitor/ingestion/`.
The FROM table depends on the query date — always use the helper, never hardcode.

#### Table Source Switch — `supervised_beeframes` vs `unified_bee_frames` (IMPORTANT)

| Date range | Table |
|---|---|
| date ≤ 2026-03-09 | `data_lake_raw_data.supervised_beeframes` |
| date ≥ 2026-03-10 | `data_lake_raw_data.unified_bee_frames` |

**Rule:** always call `raw_bee_frames_table(date)` from `src/model_monitor/ingestion/` — never hardcode either table name.

---

### 3. Ground Truth (`ground_truth/ground_truth_statuess_ca_2026.csv`)

Human-labelled model status per group per date. Source for `extraction_plan.py`.

| Column | Values | Description |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| `date` | `YYYY-MM-DD` | The evaluation date |
| `group_id` | int | Beekeeper group |
| `status` | `valid` / `invalid` / `needs_recalibration` | Human ground truth label |

**51 groups, 643 labelled dates** (as of 2026-03-26).

