## Two-Layer Architecture

```
Raw sensor data (per sensor, per group, per date)
        │
        ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Layer 1: sensor_group_segment  (per SENSOR)        │
│  "Does this sensor's physics match the predicted    │
│   hive size (small / medium / large)?"              │
│  Output: PASS / WARNING / FAIL per sensor           │
│  Data unit: individual sensor (~341K rows total)    │
│  Skill: skills/sensor_group_segment/                │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
        │  aggregate per (group_id, date)
        ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Layer 2: group_model_temperature_health            │
│           (per GROUP per DATE)  ← NOT YET BUILT     │
│  "Is the model valid for this group today?"         │
│  Output: VALID / INVALID per (group_id, date)       │
│  Ground truth: ground_truth/ CSV                    │
│  Skill: skills/group_model_temperature_health/      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

